{"tid":349781,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[JS5200]JUPAS科大工程新生討論區","createTime":"2017-08-06T18:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T01:46:30.000Z","uid":106131,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f84a583bde071ebc843d3aa3d37fb21fb4044573","tid":349781,"uid":106131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:50:48.000Z","msg":"[JS5200]JUPAS科大工程新生討論區<br />\n1.\t各位成功收到JUPAS FIRST ROUND嘅你地，記得係8月8號5pm之前交五千大元嘅留位費。交錢詳情可以去返<a href=\"http://www.jupas.edu.hk/misc/MR/course_info/JS5200.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jupas.edu.hk%2Fmisc%2FMR%2Fcourse_info%2FJS5200.htm&d=nNcQ2isqBi7IpGb3N8dlbv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=4b0e1b1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jupas.edu.hk/misc/MR/course_info/JS5200.htm</a><br />\n到睇。<br />\n2.\t交完留位費之後有幾樣野可以做左先：<br />\n(a)準備一張證件相嘅softcopy，往年都有俾你返去學校即場影學生證相嘅步驟，今年唔知會唔會有，但係通常影得出黎都好撚柒，由於張相跟足你四年，所以最好事前執靚自己少少影完自己交上去，咁樣張學生證就見得人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(b)事先睇定黎緊YR 1有咩course 可以讀/要讀，因為你地將要係9號同埋10號排左你想讀嘅course嘅次序。<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1o0xCi4OrEJXfIBPdaaDbxPmEyRl5nLParLNu7iyFbc0/edit?pli=1%3Cbr%20/%3E#heading=h.cjm9x2njevnb \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1o0xCi4OrEJXfIBPdaaDbxPmEyRl5nLParLNu7iyFbc0%2Fedit%3Fpli%3D1%253Cbr%2520%2F%253E%23heading%3Dh.cjm9x2njevnb%20&d=nNcQ2isqBi7IpGb3N8dlbv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ca7d147b\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1o0xCi4OrEJXfIBPdaaDbxPmEyRl5nLParLNu7iyFbc0/edit?pli=1%3Cbr%20/%3E#heading=h.cjm9x2njevnb </a><br />\n呢一個係幾年前有心巴打們整落嘅course簡介，少部份內容可能outdate自己衡量啦。<br />\n如果你已經有想揀嘅MAJOR 可以去返<br />\n<a href=\"http://prog-crs.ust.hk/ugprog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprog-crs.ust.hk%2Fugprog&d=nNcQ2isqBi7IpGb3N8dlbv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d753aaa5\" target=\"_blank\">http://prog-crs.ust.hk/ugprog</a><br />\n睇下有咩可以讀左先，詳情唔多講，因為遲早都會知。<br />\n<br />\n3.\tREG DAY流程<br />\n(a)知道自己Student ID Number同埋拎學生證<br />\n(b)Activate ITSC Account，itsc ac 係一個跟足你自己四年嘅ac所以密碼改完唔好唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(c)揀Peer Mentor，呢一個係有一個Mentor 一年內一定要見兩次定唔知三次嘅野，主要係幫你解答揀major/reg course嘅問題，顏色可以鳩揀，呢兩年好似會送返件tee俾你咁樣，今年唔知有冇，但係我覺得實際作用唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，倒不如直接上連登問好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n(d)reg科（好似一定要9號10號之內搞掂），SENG(school of engineering)好似係E2I(Center for Engineering Education Innovation)設立左面對面嘅consult ，reg錯course,讀到爛grade悔終生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(e)報OCAMP，科大OCAMP可以分為幾類：<br />\nSchool societies: MEMBER 主要係對應返SCHOOL嘅人, <br />\n關ENGINE事嘅只有<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">(ESU)The Engineering Students' Union </span><br />\n組爸媽同埋上莊果堆都來自不同major,未諗好咩major可以玩esu識下多d唔同major嘅人,可能好過你上網做research揀咩major.<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">(Dep soc)Departmental Societis</span>: <br />\n組爸媽同埋上莊果堆都係果一科嘅人為主,而YR1嘅你地基本上所有ENGINE Dep soc都玩得,因為未揀major,但係揀左major之後因為未必讀返果科,所以慎重揀邊個Dep soc玩,因為你玩呢一個Soc,yr2之後,同果堆人唔係讀同一科好大可能會疏遠左.<br />\n咁engine 每個dept基本上都有對應soc:civil,cs,ee,ielm,mech,cbme,cpeg<br />\n玩邊一個ocamp就自己決定啦,識返同一個major嘅人都幾重要,FYP又好,一齊上堂又好.<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">(ICA)Independent Clubs Association and Independent Clubs (興趣soc)</span><br />\n唔係每一個ICA都會搞OCAMP,去REG DAY之前就自己做下功課先啦<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">(SA)Sports Association and Sports Clubs</span><br />\nSA就不得不提dance soc, dance soc係少數會搞ocamp嘅sa soc之一,<del><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">(想玩就去玩啦(因為好多囡囡))</span></span></del><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">House Associations </span><br />\n有ocamp嘅house只有1-5<br />\n主要都係睇你出年想reg邊座hall玩返果一個hall嘅ocamp識返果堆人<br />\nhall1-5有咩特別唔多講,上面個google doc有少少資料,自己睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4.\t正式註冊左之後可以做嘅野：<br />\nREG HALL(8月10號之前):<a href=\"http://shrl.ust.hk/eng/individual.php?catid=3&amp;sid=18&amp;tid=73&amp;id=128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshrl.ust.hk%2Feng%2Findividual.php%3Fcatid%3D3%26sid%3D18%26tid%3D73%26id%3D128&d=nNcQ2isqBi7IpGb3N8dlbv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=dffb4d88\" target=\"_blank\">http://shrl.ust.hk/eng/individual.php?catid=3&amp;sid=18&amp;tid=73&amp;id=128</a><br />\n注意黎緊Freshman學校只會保證你有一個SEM嘅HALL，除非你距離夠遠又或者參加今年一個新嘅FYE Program，而被選中嘅FYE Program參加者（因為只有600位，所以極有可能會抽籤），需要參加一個compulsory嘅OCAMP(18-19/8)(兩日一夜)。<br />\n<br />\n如果有咩問題歡迎係下面問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能未來有更多補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c032b506ae5f1a016f4bb958b79a3938cf7b2f85","tid":349781,"uid":69292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T19:00:18.000Z","msg":"釘嫂打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84db8deaaf343e559f1454d1b494585267342ed8","tid":349781,"uid":106131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T02:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>釘嫂打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n事實係多囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf03e0aace98dfaf6ca9f27c8078a0f390b5b3b4","tid":349781,"uid":106131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc74ae932014198603339762c941f53f5441b05","tid":349781,"uid":106131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:51:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1BYY1phjo67e457_00Q499TfzipABQeSZEfr186HmMFE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1BYY1phjo67e457_00Q499TfzipABQeSZEfr186HmMFE&d=nNcQ2isqBi7IpGb3N8dlbv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=48e356fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1BYY1phjo67e457_00Q499TfzipABQeSZEfr186HmMFE</a><br />\n係隔離post見到 有興趣可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fd2690d3afb6d56c53898b1ba78eec77c47537","tid":349781,"uid":128241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"打手feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea19f4f86b7f2b8f4b2c30498f4bba5c940ed73","tid":349781,"uid":33631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9593b783a16c48f5319e5d5d6602adee52b99a0f","tid":349781,"uid":83210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/131305_968f6dd919338f2f2a3d4ea91daaa34e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F131305_968f6dd919338f2f2a3d4ea91daaa34e.jpg&h=ea0e1469&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d7b6171b96ddbaf57e94a19e7588dabb6329d55","tid":349781,"uid":106131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:57:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/131305_968f6dd919338f2f2a3d4ea91daaa34e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F131305_968f6dd919338f2f2a3d4ea91daaa34e.jpg&h=ea0e1469&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n交5000蚊最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d9de5e7e6f92f45f809a0cf83f82a68ac32f9a","tid":349781,"uid":69292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:23:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/131305_968f6dd919338f2f2a3d4ea91daaa34e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F131305_968f6dd919338f2f2a3d4ea91daaa34e.jpg&h=ea0e1469&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n2013<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5315ee9f535e9cb455b8e8644689a99d5cf16f","tid":349781,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:13:32.000Z","msg":"冇人嘅"},{"pid":"f58fb1dc7670c3457016ebe21f5f2d2566fd52ee","tid":349781,"uid":28250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:16:44.000Z","msg":"各位新生：<br />\n若要生活好<br />\n咪撚讀Civil!<br />\n切記 切記！"},{"pid":"1cb669157f29d3fc43e35613aa39bb1451f5041b","tid":349781,"uid":33631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:18:30.000Z","msg":"給我一個土！"},{"pid":"27ef2bc2d20f9b94d221eabb2a1848e50cf97b0c","tid":349781,"uid":106131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:58:18.000Z","msg":"有得玩好玩埋呢大半個月喇<br />\n開左SEM,想打飛機都冇時間啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e07bb17ff425baedb61ff76e5e5c9ce1c90e84","tid":349781,"uid":109687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:13:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有得玩好玩埋呢大半個月喇<br />\n開左SEM,想打飛機都冇時間啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nust有咁癲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb0bc7ea3e3b8c3327a5815354402036c75a5eb","tid":349781,"uid":106131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T14:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有得玩好玩埋呢大半個月喇<br />\n開左SEM,想打飛機都冇時間啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nust有咁癲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主要都係睇你自己目標"},{"pid":"6b1f06f63f38f53818d6c7f9f267b91c3b2d48d1","tid":349781,"uid":106131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be17f75986cdb7efac715a339e65632cbd39681f","tid":349781,"uid":106131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3578ce55c87403409b61d6f5945a340a07eff256","tid":349781,"uid":50635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847056f506c51eb540be64481ba39195c9f40950","tid":349781,"uid":106131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c96b1ebe7d6ce7fe2d0fb2da53ce53727b6eaa","tid":349781,"uid":131524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:19:59.000Z","msg":"NonJu撚LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aeb4d7645c1043ca222cc3e63f5622c31c0a99c","tid":349781,"uid":106131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T12:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3631d834e4d1d679bbb1cacfe0676b0cf2142ab6","tid":349781,"uid":109687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T12:27:08.000Z","msg":"Year 1 報咩ocamp好？"},{"pid":"ae8a9594dabe7a7c76831f89a32d164eca374455","tid":349781,"uid":106131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T12:42:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Year 1 報咩ocamp好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nengine 仔咪撚咁on9報 bsu / Busi soc ocamp<br />\n報返school/dept soc 識返同major 人<br />\n<br />\n有特定興趣例如dance soc 天文 義工soc 等等<br />\n都可以考慮下"},{"pid":"8bffdce570201d034c462ce19971b0bfc71c60a1","tid":349781,"uid":69292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Year 1 報咩ocamp好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nengine 仔咪撚咁on9報 bsu / Busi soc ocamp<br />\n報返school/dept soc 識返同major 人<br />\n<br />\n有特定興趣例如dance soc 天文 義工soc 等等<br />\n都可以考慮下</blockquote><br />\n唔想爛撚哂grade就咪撚玩hall<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}